Package com.da.antiphish.corpus

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccuracyCalculator
    AccuracyCalculator calculates the accuracy of the whole system based on a corpus analysis JSON file and saves results (accuracy, true positive, false negative, true negative and false positive rate) in an own JSON file.
    CorpusAnalyser
    CorpusAnalyser analyses a corpus of legitimate and phishing websites and stores for each analysed website all task results in an own JSON file.
    CorpusAnalysisEntry
    CorpusAnalysisEntry represents an entry of an analysed website and includes the following information: url: the URL of the analysed website phishing: indicator if analysed website is a phishing or legitimate site taskResults: map of all task results of the analysis
    CorpusAnalysisUpdater
    CorpusAnalysisUpdater analyses the specified corpus with the specified task and updates the specified corpus analysis JSON file accordingly.
    CorpusCollector
    CorpusCollector collects a training corpus of 10.000 phishing and 10.000 legitimate sites and a test corpus of 4.000 phishing and 4.000 legitimate sites.
    DomainAgeTaskThresholdCalculator
    DomainAgeTaskThresholdCalculator calculates the best domain age threshold between 0 and 12 for task DomainAgeTask based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file.
    DotsTaskThresholdCalculator
    DotsTaskThresholdCalculator calculates the best dots threshold between 0 and 20 for task DotsTask based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file.
    EmptyLinksTaskThresholdCalculator
    EmptyLinksTaskThresholdCalculator calculates the best empty links rate threshold between 0.0 and 1.0 for task EmptyLinksTask based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file.
    FormContentExtractor
    FormKeywordsExtractor extracts and counts all suspicious form keywords/contents from all forms of all phishing websites.
    MetaContentExtractor
    MetaContentExtractor extracts and counts all suspicious meta tags keywords/contents from all meta tags of all phishing websites.
    OverallThresholdCalculator
    OverallThresholdCalculator calculates the overall threshold of the whole system based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file.
    PlaintextContentExtractor
    PlaintextKeywordsExtractor extracts and counts all suspicious plaintext keywords from the whole plaintext of all phishing websites.
    PunctuationTaskThresholdCalculator
    PunctuationTaskThresholdCalculator calculates the best punctuation threshold between 0 and 50 for task PunctuationTask based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file.
    RangesCalculator
    RangesCalculator calculates the ranges for the traffic light based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file and stores the result in an own JSON file.
    ScriptContentExtractor
    ScriptContentExtractor extracts and counts all suspicious script contents from the all scirpt tags of all phishing websites.
    SingleTaskAnalyser
    SingleTaskAnalyser calculates the confidence and threshold of the specified task based on the specified corpus.
    TaskConfidenceCalculator
    TaskConfidenceCalculator calculates the confidence and threshold of each task based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file and stores the result in an own JSON file.
    TaskSafetyLimitCalculator
    TaskSafetyLimitCalculator calculates the lower and upper safety limit of each task based on the specified corpus analysis JSON file and stores the result in an own JSON file.
